2. Django Project Architecture
Q: Explain your Django project architecture.
A:

Django follows MVC (MTV) architecture: Model (data), Template (UI), View (logic).

Key components: Models, Views, Templates, URLs, Forms, Middleware, Admin interface.

Database interaction via ORM.

Settings for environment config, static/media files handling.

Example: User authentication, REST API endpoints, admin dashboard.



